  title = {{{IL23R}} ({{Interleukin}} 23 {{Receptor}}) {{Variants Protective}} against {{Inflammatory Bowel Diseases}} ({{IBD}}) {{Display Loss}} of {{Function}} Due to {{Impaired Protein Stability}} and {{Intracellular Trafficking}}},
  author = {Sivanesan, Durga and Beauchamp, Claudine and Quinou, Christiane and Lee, Jonathan and Lesage, Sylvie and Chemtob, Sylvain and Rioux, John D. and Michnick, Stephen W.},
